title: Unit #315- Brooks-Corner Unit-Historic Brick
map_address: Central Ave NE near 7th St NE
posting_body: ['Schedule a tour today!', 'Built in 1897 and 1909, these buildings have been tastefully brought into the 21st Century and converted into a mix of Studios, 1 bedrooms, and 2 bedroom units ranging in size from 562 to 1262 Sq.', 'Ft, featuring historic elements such as exposed brick and timber, in addition to concrete floors, while enjoying modern 21st century amenities such as central air and heat, and washer/dryer in unit.', 'Our residents enjoy a long range of amenities including underground parking, bike storage, private lounge, expansive fitness center and a roof deck with', 'downtown views - just to name a few.', 'APARTMENT FEATURES:', '• Premium appliance package: French door fridge, front loading washer/dryer.', '• Modern kitchen cabinets with wine rack.', '• Quartz counter-tops.', '• Garbage disposal.', '• Exposed historic brick.', '• Large walk in closet.', '• Linen closet in bathroom.', '• Sealed concrete floors.', '• Concrete construction.', '• Onsite Maintenance', 'BUILDING AMENITIES:', '• Fitness center with free weights, cardio machines, TRX full body work out system, and 12 weight machines.', '• Indoor heated parking.(additional cost)', '• Sky Deck with kitchen, outdoor patio, grills, 180-degree skyline views, and outdoor fireplace.', '• LaBelle Lounge featuring shuffleboard, Billiards table, kitchen and gathering nooks.', '• Dog friendly with "pocket park" onsite and dog spa.', '• Additional storage lockers available.(additional cost)', '• Ample bike storage with "Fit it" station.', '• Lively neighborhood including shopping dining and nightlife just steps from your door.', '• Blocks from Mississippi river and recreational trails.', 'OUR COMPANY:', "We've been doing this for a long time.", 'Steven Scott Management, Inc. has been successfully managing rental communities in the Twin Cities of Minneapolis and St. Paul for more than 50 years and is one of the largest locally owned property management firms in Minnesota.', 'We care.', 'We know that renting an apartment is about finding your home - a place you are proud of and a place you can relax and feel comfortable.', "We don't take this responsibility lightly.", 'Steven Scott Management', '700 Central Avenue NE', 'Minneapolis, MN 55414', 'show contact info']
